---

<html lang="ja">
  <Head
    title="About me | Akitoshi Lab."
    description="ロボットが大好きな大学生です．思ったことや日常の出来事をつぶやきます．たまに技術．"
    ogImage="https://images.microcms-assets.io/assets/a1f82a67495a4c7c8cd02269aa346701/1b10a9dfa3dc476cb8a9154521d1f4bb/OGP.webp"
  />
  <body class="m-0 p-0 font-snself overflow-x-hidden">
    <Header />
    <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto pt-10 pb-12">
      <astro-island>
        <Card />
      </astro-island>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl mb-4">About Blog</h2>
        <hr class="border-gray-400 mb-4" />
        <p>
          このブログ(akitoshi-lab.com)は，@konoe_aktoshiが日常で感じたことやひらめいたことを書いている”メモ帳”です．
        </p>
        <p>
          もちろん，技術的なことも書きますが，必ずしも正しいとは限りません．私が小さい脳で一生懸命考えてやったことの備忘録です．
        </p>
        <a
          href={config.social.buyMeACoffee}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <img
            height="40"
            alt="Buy Me A Coffee"
            src="https://cdn.buymeacoffee.com/buttons/v2/default-yellow.png"
            class="mt-4"
          />
        </a>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl mb-4">サイト環境</h2>
        <hr class="border-gray-400 mb-4" />
        <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">物理環境</h3>
        <p>Yamaha RTX1210</p>
        <p>Dell S6010-on</p>
        <p>HPE DL360 gen8</p>
        <p>Dell R620</p>
        <p>Dell R720xd</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">計算環境</h3>
        <p>Ubuntu Server</p>
        <p>Nginx</p>
        <p>Nuxt3</p>
        <p>Micro CMS</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl mb-4">資格</h2>
        <hr class="border-gray-400 mb-4" />
        <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Credly</h3>
        <!-- badge1 -->
        <div
          data-iframe-width="150"
          data-iframe-height="270"
          data-share-badge-id="6ff7b8a5-c4c8-4d1d-a683-071162cb3a5f"
          data-share-badge-host="https://www.credly.com"
        >
        </div>
        <script
          type="text/javascript"
          async
          src="//cdn.credly.com/assets/utilities/embed.js"
        ></script>
        <!-- badge2 -->
        <div
          data-iframe-width="150"
          data-iframe-height="270"
          data-share-badge-id="dc1e577a-c863-4c11-8377-b51780f429ec"
          data-share-badge-host="https://www.credly.com"
        >
        </div>
        <script
          type="text/javascript"
          async
          src="//cdn.credly.com/assets/utilities/embed.js"
        ></script>

        <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">No Badge</h3>
        <p>第四級アマチュア無線技士</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl mb-4">Works</h2>
        <hr class="border-gray-400 mb-4" />
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          {
            works.map((work) => (
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
                <Image
                  src={work.image}
                  alt="work image"
                  class="w-full h-40 object-cover"
                />
                <div class="p-4 flex flex-col justify-between">
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">{work.title}</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">{work.desc}</p>
                  </div>
                  {work.prizes.length > 0 && (
                    <div class="flex items-center mt-4">
                      <span class="i-material-symbols-rewarded-ads-outline-rounded text-yellow-500 mr-2" />
                      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                        {work.prizes.map((prize, i) => (
                          <li class="text-sm">{prize}</li>
                        ))}
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  )}
                </div>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl mb-4">Profile</h2>
        <hr class="border-gray-400 mb-4" />
        <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Affiliated</h3>
        <span class="i-hugeicons-university"></span>
        <p>電気通信大学</p>
        <span class="i-bi-pc-display"></span>
        <p>MMA</p>
        <p>Scramble</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Prize</h3>
        <table class="w-full table-auto mt-4">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-700 text-white">年度</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-700 text-white">イベント名</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-700 text-white">受賞内容</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {
              skillSet.map((item) => (
                <tr>
                  <td class="border px-4 py-2">{item.since}</td>
                  <td class="border px-4 py-2">{item.by}</td>
                  <td class="border px-4 py-2">{item.name}</td>
                </tr>
              ))
            }
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
